Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說會送到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者寄出的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死神送來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著「有您的郵件  請蓋章」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啦  據說是個女孩子送過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這裡是再開發區域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是附近有人  務必向他們打聽下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  人類  真是麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼活著時不說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有只有死後才說得出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  翔太的字寫的還真爛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如這個  怎麼讀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是su啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以發明新文字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小心點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我重要的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  雖說讓火箭升空很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是多練練字比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚴格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會會長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  會長本來就是遭人怨恨的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你很能說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時說得多的都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾  綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  早就想說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對綾瀨…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的  我是綾瀨明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  妹妹那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  知道了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸…被找到的時候已經是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}海鷗市警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾  綾  綾瀨  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察局的人說會送我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現的遺體是住在三上鎮的無業者綾瀨竹藏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,45歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}海鷗市  發現男性屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨先生是8號失蹤的  家人向警方提出過搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  0913
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這可不是我的錯  真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  還有一個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛確實有兩個聲音的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來送信的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是綾瀨明日奈的戀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀  戀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和綾瀨在不同的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是在不同的學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是在這棟大樓裡相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始第一輪噴射測試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5  4  3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後  綾瀨變得經常來看火箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔～  邂逅嗎  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  每次我都很頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為怎麼解釋她都弄不清火箭的構造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  單相思麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你這麼直接說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信…如果是綾瀨明日奈的戀人會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是綾瀨竹藏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹…綾瀨的爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺言？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從死後的世界寄來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  稱為死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者最後留下的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  死者怎麼會寫信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有身體  巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體的話  當然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後的世界也分等級的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到 level 4 為止  都有身體的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以寫字  還可以吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杖…在說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才開始就在說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅能說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是站著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他說你是『巫女』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你違反了業務規定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不能遵守規定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不過是個備置品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把人家當物品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是單純的杖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在變成人的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}難道真的是杖在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨明日奈沒有戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信地址不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有收信人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信  由我接收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒　我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有聽見我們說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信人是綾瀨明日奈的戀人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是這樣合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  那封信沒寄到人手上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不去接收綾瀨父親想傳達的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來成為她的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你們就無話可說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不錯  你還真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  不錯嘛  男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛  是青春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  真是青澀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心地放進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊  裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再用膠帶封好  記得寫上名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你那邊…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『深表遺憾』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說像大人一樣說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  沒聯絡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙著辦市政府那邊的手續什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的　那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊才辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦  意外的輕鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我還很堅強的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨  要是我有什麼可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還是讓姊姊來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  下次再說可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點忙亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我有重要的話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…雖然這種時候有點不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  喜  喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡  歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭馬上就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道你很忙  但要不要來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會等你來了再發射的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  要升空了啊　火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼要是火箭完成了發短信給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼掛掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉碎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}意指翔太告白後被拒絕  然後自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這種不吉利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事  時機是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  聽好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂人的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不面對面跟對方說是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子  也不喜歡在電話裡被告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  你打算在火箭升空的那一刻告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那種火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  要是發射失敗了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很尷尬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  火箭發射和告白一起緩緩進行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啪地一聲爆炸也挺華麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好嘛  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭又不是焰火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成功升空的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送成給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到衛星軌道上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的感情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  覺得自己剛才那句話很帥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個一起達成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  是杖就別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杖  是卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音局  第92點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  話說你們在別人的地盤上放一堆煙出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自以為是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}看來這份工作得延長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種廢品蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}發誓 一定成功發射！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦　謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得取個名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點做過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  她說過他妹妹叫美紅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自言自語些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 卡娜卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杖還要睡覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暫停活動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說她像人類那樣在睡覺的話  她會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒　真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於死後文  你為什麼相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人不會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也沒被人信任過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是「高中生是不可能成功發射火箭的」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨卻相信了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說「好厲害」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想看升空的那一刻」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我想也試著去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真單純
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過單純才美好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家是在明天是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知過別人了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校聯絡過了　我沒什麼親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到…還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要到明天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白之時～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是文伽讓他想告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想看到死後文送達不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我職業責任感強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和卡娜卡不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  不是還有在用的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探險終於有收效了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等、等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多探險下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太也需要獨處的時間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把信放在翔太那了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音局的指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太  你已經看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  什麼啊這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是問你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡作劇也要有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨…怎麼會殺掉自己父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著殺死自己的是女兒明日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  還特意要女兒的戀人告發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死  會讓人變得坦誠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔也好  怨恨也好  所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從死後的世界寄來的信？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你的我真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:18:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bye bye  美紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能找到我家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你告訴過我地址
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到你妹妹呢  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  只剩我們兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家沒有媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和市政局的人商量過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們進福利機構了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不上高中了  要去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼大學啦夢想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望妹妹有想做的事情時因為沒錢而不得不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太也是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力做自己喜歡的事不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  綾瀨不可能是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
